<div class="bg-purple-900 h-64 home--main home--bg">
  <div class="lg:container flex justify-end items-center h-full flex-col">
    <div class="shadow bg-white flex gap-8 p-8 items-center flex-col lg:flex-row w-full lg:w-3/4">
      <div>The week-long event spotlights amazing work from over a dozen categories including live, face-to-face events,
